# Backend API URL
# For local development, copy this file to .env and uncomment:
# NUXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE=http://localhost:8000
#
# For production (e.g. if you deploy the backend on Render), set this
# as an environment variable in Vercel:
# NUXT_PUBLIC_API_BASE=https://your-backend-url.onrender.com
#
# If left empty, the frontend works fully on its own.
# The opt-in comparison feature just shows "backend offline".
